  "keyFeatures": [
    "Unified API V2 with a single key for 60+ EVM chains",
    "Normal, internal, ERC20, ERC721, and ERC1155 transaction history",
    "Smart contract ABI retrieval and source code verification",
    "Gas Oracle and real-time gas price recommendations",
    "Address metadata: nametags, labels, and entity categorization",
    "Advanced filters for multi-address transaction queries",
    "JSON-RPC proxy endpoints (eth_call, eth_getBlockByNumber, etc.)",
    "Historical token balances, supply, and holder data (PRO)",
    "Daily network statistics and analytics (PRO)",
    "Model Context Protocol (MCP) server for AI integration"
  ],
